Package com.tejasmehta.OdometryCore.localization

A package to handle localization of various numerical positions and angular units into an easily recognizable abstraction

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EncoderPositions
    A class to unify all three encoder positions used in the core calculations for both general convenience and lack of confusion over multiple values
    OdometryPosition
    A class to store the Odometry position in the format of an x coordinate, a a y coordinate, and an angle measure with it's heading unit, either a degree or radian.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HeadingUnit
    An enumeration for the heading unit used in the OdometryPosition to allow any users to request their degree/heading be given in the following unit(s)
